            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <strong>beef stock mix </strong>and the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>harissa paste</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> in a large heatproof bowl</p><p>Add the <strong>couscous</strong>, cover and set aside</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
